  "description": "The Secret Ingredient: Empathy\nThe true delight of Wander Scoop lies in the heartwarming cutscenes and dialogues. Every quirky character who slides onto a stool carries a personal puzzle and different ice cream flavours, and the process of making them serves as a metaphor for life’s challenges and joys. \n\nLevel Up Your Cosy Kingdom\nFortunately, guiding souls and making people happy can also be profitable! As you ace those metaphorical mix-ups and sell your legendary treats, you'll earn money and gain the experience needed to upgrade your arsenal of ingredients and equipment, as well as decorate your parlour.\n\nA Feast for the Eyes and Soul\nSink into a world rendered in a beautiful, colourful, and inviting pastel art style. Everything is soft, rounded, and comforting. Every detail, from the gentle texture of the whipped cream to the subtle shimmer of the ice crystals, is designed to give you a warm hug in game form.\n\nCome on in. The scoop is waiting to be wielded.\n\nKEY FEATURES: \n- 10 unique, flavourful customers to meet and learn their stories\n- Tons of delicious new ingredients, equipment, and décor items to be unlocked\n- Delightful pastel art style \n- Sweet, cosy atmosphere, encouraging to cherish the simple joys of life\n- Smooth, relaxing music",
